name: Boogie#1 StraweberryFields 2021/3.3MB
description: StrawberryFields is the 1st digitally manipulated image of the “Boogie” gif-series and originates from a painting. Like the domino effect, this series emerges as a coherent sequence, a kind of chain reaction in which the previous work forms the starting point for the next. The finished series is then to be understood as a closed information cycle.
